_sText:
Hi guys.

I hope, here is the last version on paper.
The map is 3x bigger than the first version, i think the gameplay is really better. I can say that it is my best map, and maybe one of the best jailbreak map i have seen.

Games
==================
12 games. I guess it's good for a map :)
- Dodge : You have to dodge some plane, which are coming in front of you. Plus there is a little "laser" on the floor to make the game harder.

- The Race : It's not a bhop, it's a long race, winners are teleported. Be carefull, players can climb on the CT zone.

- The swimming pool : Here you can do loooot of race, mainly with the slide ;)
- Disco with 4 songs

- Bomb / freestyle : The area in the swimming pool where you can climb on everywall.

- The site : It's a climb / race.

- Right/left : You press the button, and Ts have to run to the right side. Cts have to kill the last T.

- Hunger Game : Simple area with teamkilling :)


Secrets
==================
In this map there are looooot of secret and special weapons.
The main part of them come from an other map, but the creator don't want to be credited, but thank you anyway :].
There are lot of "sounds" with theses weapons, unfortunatly, they are in french, and i will try to translate them asap.

You will find :

- The Holy bible
- The BIG GUN
- The Car
- The penis
- The lemon gang (Yeah like in ze_paper..)


Have fun :)
